{"title":"使用U盘扩容openwrt的根目录","uid":"d3f1fcc92d8224fd08a939609fc949fc","slug":"openwrt-1","date":"2023-06-09T10:48:10.000Z","updated":"2024-01-03T08:51:51.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/openwrt-1.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"1-格式化U盘为Ext4的格式\"><a href=\"#1-格式化U盘为Ext4的格式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.格式化U盘为Ext4的格式\"></a>1.格式化U盘为Ext4的格式</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mkfs.ext4 &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda1</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"2-执行以下命令将原根目录的文件拷贝到u盘\"><a href=\"#2-执行以下命令将原根目录的文件拷贝到u盘\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.执行以下命令将原根目录的文件拷贝到u盘\"></a>2.执行以下命令将原根目录的文件拷贝到u盘</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">mkdir -p &#x2F;tmp&#x2F;introot\nmkdir -p &#x2F;tmp&#x2F;extroot\nmount --bind &#x2F; &#x2F;tmp&#x2F;introot\nmount &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda1 &#x2F;tmp&#x2F;extroot\ntar -C &#x2F;tmp&#x2F;introot -cvf - . | tar -C &#x2F;tmp&#x2F;extroot -xf -\numount &#x2F;tmp&#x2F;introot\numount &#x2F;tmp&#x2F;extroot</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"3-使用blkid命令来查看sda1的UUID-结果如下\"><a href=\"#3-使用blkid命令来查看sda1的UUID-结果如下\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.使用blkid命令来查看sda1的UUID,结果如下:\"></a>3.使用<code>blkid</code>命令来查看sda1的UUID,结果如下:</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">&#x2F;dev&#x2F;mtdblock5: TYPE&#x3D;&quot;squashfs&quot;\n&#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda1: UUID&#x3D;&quot;c91d06ce-8781-4255-b635-610bd6beef7e&quot; TYPE&#x3D;&quot;ext4&quot;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"4-修改-etc-config-fstab文件\"><a href=\"#4-修改-etc-config-fstab文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.修改/etc/config/fstab文件\"></a>4.修改<code>/etc/config/fstab</code>文件</h2><p>将以下配置拷贝到文件末尾,uuid替换为你自己的uuid</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">config &#39;mount&#39;\n         option  target  &#39;&#x2F;&#39;\n         option  uuid    &#39;c91d06ce-8781-4255-b635-610bd6beef7e&#39;         \n         option  enabled &#39;1&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"5-使用reboot命令重启openwrt系统\"><a href=\"#5-使用reboot命令重启openwrt系统\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.使用reboot命令重启openwrt系统\"></a>5.使用<code>reboot</code>命令重启openwrt系统</h2>","text":"1.格式化U盘为Ext4的格式mkfs.ext4 &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sda1 2.执行以下命令将原根目录的文件拷贝到u盘mkdir -p &#x2F;tmp&#x2F;introot mkdir -p &#x2F;tmp&#x2F;extroot mount --bi...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":811,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"系统运维","slug":"系统运维","count":4,"path":"api/categories/系统运维.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"LINUX","slug":"LINUX","count":2,"path":"api/tags/LINUX.json"},{"name":"openwrt","slug":"openwrt","count":2,"path":"api/tags/openwrt.json"},{"name":"扩容","slug":"扩容","count":1,"path":"api/tags/扩容.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%E5%8C%96U%E7%9B%98%E4%B8%BAExt4%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1.格式化U盘为Ext4的格式</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E5%B0%86%E5%8E%9F%E6%A0%B9%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95%E7%9A%84%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%8B%B7%E8%B4%9D%E5%88%B0u%E7%9B%98\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2.执行以下命令将原根目录的文件拷贝到u盘</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8blkid%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E6%9D%A5%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8Bsda1%E7%9A%84UUID-%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E5%A6%82%E4%B8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3.使用blkid命令来查看sda1的UUID,结果如下:</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4-%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9-etc-config-fstab%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4.修改&#x2F;etc&#x2F;config&#x2F;fstab文件</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#5-%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8reboot%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E9%87%8D%E5%90%AFopenwrt%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">5.使用reboot命令重启openwrt系统</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"finalpi","slug":"blog-aut